<div class="container mt-4 pt-4">
    <hr style="border-top: 4px solid #708090;" />
    @{
        ViewData["Title"] = "About Me";
    }
    <h1 class="text-center">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <hr style="border-top: 4px solid #708090;" />

    <div class="row align-items-center mt-4">
        <!-- Left Column: Image -->
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <img src="~/img/James Headshot.jpg"
                 alt="James Headshot"
                 class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm"
                 style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" asp-append-version="true" />
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: About Text -->
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <p class="mt-4">
                I have a <strong>strong foundation in object-oriented programming</strong> using <strong>Java and C#</strong>, combined with
                <strong>full-stack development experience in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and SQL,</strong> 
                which has enabled the development of <strong>scalable and maintainable applications.</strong> Applying 
                <strong>Agile methodologies such as Scrum</strong> and following <strong>software development life cycle 
                (SDLC) best practices</strong> proved invaluable when working on a <strong>Project Management Tool,</strong> which 
                <strong>enhanced database integration and backend logic skills using ASP.NET and PostgreSQL.</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>